attributes.Long form description: The student assembles the table from Ikea. First, he grabs the legs and assembles them. Then tries to screw the bottom hex socket head, and the instructor tells him to flip the legs. Next, screws the top and bottom hex socket head. After that, assembles the top circle and places the top tray.
